text.tspan: Need: Biologists at the SD Zoo are interested in autonomous
behavioral tracking of animals in captivity, so that they can
more effectively monitor and improve animal welfare.
Tech: Weather-proof hardware platform with panning camera,
embedded Linux computing, 360 degree video lens,
Solution: An "Intelligent Camera Trap" that can automatically
follow an animal in it's enclosure, and annotate that footage
Remote Sensing Solutions For Cross-Disciplinary Research
